Images: ["[630_360_16814...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1681455767-875.jpg)", "[1681990365-54...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1681990365-548.jpg)"]

